race.description: The Glass Slipper Super Maiden Handicap
race.comment: ACHARNEE (5) ran a good race over this course and distance on debut and will have taken a lot from that race day experience. Hoop Morgan sticks in the saddle following that first-up runner-up finish and maps ideally for this from gate four. Will prove very hard to toss. MIND YA BIZZ (8) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in both career outings and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Has the ability to mix it with them. IMPURITEZE (11) resumes here but showed enough in her first preparation to warrant consideration in a race like this. Respect from the Freedman barn. FUADEE (1) gets a stack of weight relief with the 4kg claim and rates among the leading hopes.
